title: Subway Surfers keyboard MOD v 1.1.exe
description:
The next update to the Keyboard MOD of Subway Surfers PC game.


Put the keyboard MOD v 1.1.exe into your game folder and double click the keyboard MOD v 1.1.exe to play.

Up Arrow = Jump
Down Arrow = Roll
Right Arrow = Turn Right
Left Arrow = Turn Left
Spacebar = Hover-Board
